
                        Agenix Tutorial

Notes: 28/09/2024
Location: Nix Hacking Weekend

____________

Agenix is one of the Nix tools for secret deployment. The other tool that is 
often used is called Sops-Nix.

* The Problem And The Solution

  Currently, there is no "good" way to share secrets in NixOS. We can't store 
  *secrets* in plain text, as these would be visible to anyone that sees it. 
